nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 146 is the 124th issue of the magazine Star Wars Insider and the 54th published by Titan Magazines. It was released on December 10, 2013.

Star Wars Insider will be presenting the third and final part of their guide to Star Wars roleplaying games. Plus, they'll have the very latest news on Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens and Star Wars: Rebels!
